content:
while is a Java keyword.It starts a looping block.The general syntax of a while, using Extended Backus-Naur Form, iswhile-looping-statement ::= while condition-clause 
                                    single-statement | block-statement

condition-clause    ::= ( Boolean Expression )
single-statement    ::= Statement
block-statement     ::= { Statement [ Statements ] }For example:while ( i < maxLoopIter )
 {
    System.println("Iter=" +i++);
 }See also:Java Programming/Statements
